WAPI - Web Api

Injects html into existing nginx server and runs api endpoints on port 5001 (default)

To enable endpoints create file /mnt/local/sysconfig/endpoints.wapi and add:

export ENDPOINTS='endpoint1 endpoint2 endpoint3'

ie
acq1001_590> cat /mnt/local/sysconfig/endpoints.wapi
export ENDPOINTS='awg_composer'

